                <!-- 🔬 Arxitektura dokumentatsiyasi: T31 GitHub + T16 Fayl shifrlash -->
                <div class="ws-acc" data-group="integratsiya" data-roles="team_lead,member,admin">
                  <button type="button" class="ws-acc-head" data-acc="architecture" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="acc-architecture">🔬 Arxitektura <span class="ws-acc-ico">▸</span></button>
                  <div class="ws-acc-body" id="acc-architecture">
                    <div class="ws-acc-body-inner">
                      <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);">🐙 T31 — GitHub Issues Sync</h4>
                      <div class="ws-arch-doc">
                        <p><strong>Nima qiladi:</strong> Vazifani (task) GitHub Issues'ga issue sifatida yaratadi.</p>
                        <div class="ws-arch-flow">
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">1. Foydalanuvchi repo va tokenni kiritadi</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">2. Client → <code>POST /api/sync-github</code> (taskId, repo, token)</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step"><strong>Server:</strong> taskni Firestore'dan o'qiydi, rollarni tekshiradi</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step"><strong>Server:</strong> GitHub API'ga so'rov:<br><code>POST https://api.github.com/repos/{repo}/issues</code></span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step"><strong>Server:</strong> <code>githubIssueId</code> + <code>issueUrl</code> → task'ga yozadi</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ws-arch-details">
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-auth">Auth: <code>GITHUB_TOKEN</code> env yoki shaxsiy token</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-sec">Xavfsizlik: Token hech qayerda saqlanmaydi</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-limit">Rate limit: GitHub API 5000 req/soat</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-sec">Xatolik: 404→repo yo'q, 401→token noto'g'ri, 502→aloqa</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>

                      <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--line);margin:16px 0;">

                      <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);">🔒 T16 — Shifrlangan fayl biriktirish</h4>
                      <div class="ws-arch-doc">
                        <p><strong>Nima qiladi:</strong> Fayl brauzerda AES-256-GCM bilan shifrlanadi, so'ng Firebase Storage'ga yuklanadi. Server <strong>hech qachon</strong> ochiq faylni yoki shifr kalitini ko'rmaydi — zero-trust arxitektura.</p>
                        <div class="ws-arch-flow">
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">1. <strong>Client:</strong> Fayl tanlanadi → <code>file.arrayBuffer()</code></span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">2. <strong>Client:</strong> AES-256-GCM kaliti (32B) + IV (12B) yaratiladi:<br><code>crypto.getRandomValues()</code></span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">3. <strong>Client:</strong> Fayl shifrlanadi:<br><code>crypto.subtle.encrypt({name:'AES-GCM', iv}, key, data)</code></span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">4. <strong>Client→Storage:</strong> CIPHERTEXT → Firebase Storage<br><code>uploadBytes(storageRef, enc)</code></span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">5. <strong>Client→Server:</strong> Metadata yuboriladi:<br><code>POST /api/create-attachment</code><br><span style="color:var(--text-muted,#8b949e);font-size:12px">faqat: teamId, fileName, size, IV, versionNote<br>★ Kalit (KEY) yuborilmaydi</span></span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step"><strong>Server:</strong> Firestore'ga metadata yozadi:<br><code>attachments/{id} → {fileName, iv, size, version}</code></span>
                          <span style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-muted,#8b949e);font-size:12px;text-align:center">Server fayl byte'larini ko'rmaydi, kalitni ko'rmaydi</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-arrow">→</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-step">6. <strong>Client:</strong> Shifr kaliti faqat yuklovchiga ko'rsatiladi<br>Qabul qiluvchiga alohida ulashish kerak (Telegram/email)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin-top:12px;background:rgba(47,129,247,0.06);border-radius:12px;padding:12px;border:1px solid rgba(47,129,247,0.12)">
                          <strong style="font-size:13px">📌 Backend nima qiladi?</strong>
                          <ul style="margin:6px 0 0;padding-left:18px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted,#8b949e);line-height:1.7">
                            <li>Fayl byte'larini <strong>ko'rmaydi</strong> (Storage'ga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri client yuklaydi)</li>
                            <li>Shifr kalitini (KEY) <strong>ko'rmaydi</strong> (faqat yuklovchi biladi)</li>
                            <li>Faqat <strong>metadata</strong> saqlaydi: fileName, size, IV, version, versiya tarixi</li>
                            <li>IV (initialization vector) — deshifrlash uchun kerak, lekin kalitsiz foydasiz</li>
                            <li>Yangi versiya (T54): eski metadata <code>versions[]</code> ga arxivlanadi</li>
                          </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ws-arch-details" style="margin-top:10px">
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-crypto">Shifrlash: AES-256-GCM (Web Crypto API)</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-sec">Xavfsizlik: Server ochiq faylni ko'rmaydi (zero-trust)</span>
                          <span class="ws-arch-tag tag-ver">Versiyalash: T54 — har yangi yuklash eski versiyani saqlab qoladi</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
